    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Conical helmets constructed of a number of segments and bands, known since Roman times and in use in a modified form until the 14th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
